snippet.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution - Official Teaser Trailer (English Subtitles)
snippet.description:
The best of the Shibuya Incident arc combines with the debut of the first two episodes of Season 3's Culling Game arc in this exclusive theatrical event! Coming to North America exclusively in movie theatres starting December 5.

A veil abruptly descends over the busy Shibuya area amid the bustling Halloween crowds, trapping countless civilians inside. Satoru Gojo, the strongest jujutsu sorcerer, steps into the chaos. But lying in wait are curse users and spirits scheming to seal him away.
Yuji Itadori, accompanied by his classmates and other top-tier jujutsu sorcerers, enters the fray in an unprecedented clash of curses — the Shibuya Incident.
In the aftermath, ten colonies across Japan are transformed into dens of curses in a plan orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo, the most wicked sorcerer in history. As the deadly Culling Game starts, Special Grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu is assigned to carry out Yuji’s execution for his perceived crimes.
The desperate confrontation between Satoru Gojo’s two beloved students comes to the big screen with an early preview. Be the first to experience Yuji and Yuta’s fateful battle with the hotly anticipated kickoff to Season 3 in theatres nationwide.

#IGN #Anime

snippet.title: Saipan | Official Trailer (2025) | In Cinemas Across Ireland January 1st
snippet.description:
The thrilling story of the infamous confrontation between iconic Republic of Ireland football captain Roy Keane (Éanna Hardwicke) and his national team manager Mick McCarthy (Steve Coogan) during the Irish team’s preparations for the 2002 FIFA World Cup.

The intense rivalry between these two personalities transcended the game, gripping an entire nation and the sporting world as a whole. On the surface, the feud was all about standards, but deep down it was an incredible story of two men whose rivalry and contempt surpassed the sport they loved. This is the definitive account of one of the most fractious fallings-out in the history of sport.

Directed by Lisa Barros D'Sa & Glenn Leyburn.
Starring Éanna Hardwicke, Steve Coogan, Alice Lowe, Jamie Beamish, Alex Murphy, and Harriet Cains.

SAIPAN opens in cinemas across Ireland on January 1st 2026.

#ChooseYourSide #SaipanFilm #TeamRoy #TeamMick

snippet.title: Mortal Kombat II | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's called Mortal Kombat (II).
Mortal Kombat II – only in theatres and IMAX May 15, 2026. #MortalKombatMovie #FilmedForIMAX

From New Line Cinema comes the latest high-stakes installment in the blockbuster video game franchise in all its brutal glory, Mortal Kombat II.  This time, the fan favourite champions—now joined by Johnny Cage himself—are pitted against one another in the ultimate, no-holds barred, gory battle to defeat the dark rule of Shao Kahn that threatens the very existence of the Earthrealm and its defenders.

Karl Urban stars as Johnny Cage, alongside Adeline Rudolph, Jessica McNamee, Josh Lawson, Ludi Lin, Mehcad Brooks, Tati Gabrielle, Lewis Tan, Damon Herriman, with Chin Han, Tadanobu Asano as Lord Raiden, Joe Taslim as Bi-Han, and Hiroyuki Sanada as Hanzo Hasashi and Scorpion.

Director Simon McQuoid returns to helm the follow up to his explosive 2021 cinematic adventure, from a screenplay by Jeremy Slater, based on the videogame created by Ed Boon and John Tobias.  The film is produced by Todd Garner, James Wan, Toby Emmerich, E. Bennett Walsh and McQuoid, and executive produced by Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Slater and Lawrence Kasanoff.  

Joining McQuoid behind the camera are director of photography Stephen F. Windon, production designer Yohei Taneda, editor Stuart Levy and costume designer Cappi Ireland, with casting by Rich Delia and music by Benjamin Wallfisch.

The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, only in theatres and IMAX® across North America on May 15, 2026.

Текст:
Раз, два, три … паауу

Кой с тебе ме събра?
Ядове да бера
Обичам те ама, малко си тралала
Скучно ли ти е с мен?
Скандали сто на ден, обичам те ама майката ми аха…
Ра-та-та-та-таа

Още от малка съм луда и сладка, нали?
Но дъската хлопа ми, хлопа хлопа ми
Ако не слушаш и ходиш по чужди жени, 
бърза помощ си викни, ще боли боли 

Ръцете горе всички!

Кой с тебе ме събра?
Ядове да бера
Обичам те ама малко си тралала 
Скучно ли ти е с мен? 
Скандали сто на ден, 
обичам те ама майката ми аха…

Кво ти е бе мило?
Казах ти нищо!
Ех от твоето нищо лошо ми е пак
Няма да сме ние, ако не се скараме.
Няма да сме ние, ако не се блокираме.
И в кревата, и в муската, да знаеш само аз съм най-добрата!
Балканска двойка, куче и котка.
Той е с анцунг, аз пък с рокля.

Раз, два, три, пауу

Кой с тебе ме събра?
Ядове да бера
Обичам те ама малко си тралала 
Скучно ли ти е с мен? 
Скандали сто на ден, обичам те ама майката ми аха…

В къщата мъжа съм аз.
Става квото кажа аз.
За БМВ пари спестих, питах жената.
И нии решихме!

Кой с тебе ме събра?
Ядове да бера
Обичам те ама малко си тралала 
Скучно ли ти е с мен? 
Скандали сто на ден, обичам те ама майката ми аха…

snippet.title: Ziggy, the Master of Thunder! (New Brawler Animation)
snippet.description:
The Great Ziggy Show starts now! 🤘

🌹 Collect 14 Ziggy Boxes during the Brawler Event to unlock him!
🪄 Get a Ziggy Box for every 2 wins
🐆 You have 3 daily tickets (which reset each day, no stacking!)
🪞 Try Ziggy for free in Mirror Matches!
✨ Ziggy will go to the Starr Road on November 6th, a few hours before the next Brawl Pass Season starts. This is a change from the previous Brawler release event and is part of testing different Brawler release setups. This likely won't change the way the Brawler release event works, since the focus is more on testing different dates and timelines throughout a season and update cycle and we will be trying a few different options in upcoming Brawler releases before committing to a specific format

Song composed and performed by Reckless Love 🎶
